📍 When we go to downtown Toronto for events we love to stay somewhere with a great location. The @westinharbourcastle is right on Lake Ontario with amazing views with lakefront rooms.

🏷️ This is the perfect hotel when attending an event at the Rogers Centre or Scotiabank or just simply for a night out on the town!

🌆 If your wanting to stay in for the evening the hotel has a breathtaking pool and hot tub with glass windows with an incredible view of the lake on one side and the city on the other.

🍳We can’t forget the breakfast buffet which was a perfect exit before our morning checkout

social_posts.post_text:
Let your vacation start early at the @sheratongatewaytoronto 

📍 This newly transformed hotel is located right at terminal 3 at the Toronto Pearson Airport! 

✈️ You are just steps from your departure and a short train link away from terminal one!

🏨 Located in the hotel is a coffee shop, restaurant and the Sheraton club which we recommend for your staycation: offers snacks + hot meals + drinks 24/7 
You will feel relaxed and recharged after your stay for your travel day ahead!

#sheraton #sheratongatewaytoronto #toronto #yyz #airport #hotel #travel #travelphotography

📍Phoenix Arizona
Surrounded by mountain views, this resort is a 20 minute drive North of downtown Phoenix. 

@hiltonphoenixtapatio 

This insane resort has hiking trails with direct access from the property! We definitely took full advantage and hiked these trails. (Don’t forget water!) 

Things to do:
Golf ⛳️ 
Swimming 🏊🏻‍♀️ 
On Site Restaurant 🍽️
Fitness Center 🏋🏼‍♀️ 
Room Service 🛎️ 
Spa 🧖🏼‍♀️ 
Tennis 🎾 

The on site restaurant is located at the top of the hills where you will be driven to by the free resort shuttle. We thoroughly enjoyed dinner & drinks up there while watching the sunset behind the mountains ⛰️ 

Would you stay at this incredible resort during your visit to Phoenix? 

#hiltonphoenixtapatio #tapatiocliffshilton #hiltonhotels #travel

🏷️ Save this for your next trip to Scottsdale Arizona. This restaurant is SO cute and has the most delicious cocktails. They have a bucket of beer + mini margaritas on special. 🍹 These we’re the perfect shareables to go with our yummy appetizers 🍽️ 📌 @blancotacostequila  #arizona #scottsdale #travel #blancotacosandtequila
You have to add Arizona to your bucket list! This place was truly magical 🌵#arizona #travel #travelphotography #instatravel

SCOTTSDALE: where to stay + eat

Where to stay 📌 Hilton Scottsdale Resort & Villas @hilton.scottsdale 

The perfect location in the ❤️ of Scottsdale. Surrounded by a ton of restaurants and shops.

We loved the complimentary shuttle that took us to old town Scottsdale for the real city experience. Another highlight was the palm tree filled pool area where we spent our day relaxing under the hot Arizona sun 🌵 

Where to eat: 🌮 🍹 

With SO many choices we recommend to check out @jojo.coffeehouse for the best coffee flights and brunch ☕️ 🍳 

@almascottsdale for the best margarita flights + dinner 🍹 

@blacotacostequila for a fun vibe with amazing tacos and drink specials! 🌮 

Would you stay here? #arizona #hilton #travel #travelblogger #travelphotography #travelling #hotelblogger #hosted #hiltonblogger #torontoblogger #niagarablogger #scottsdaleaz

📌 Things to do when you stay at the @thecottagebycallisto this summer 

🍷 Visit Prince Edward County where you can visit some amazing wineries, breweries, and some beautiful beaches 

📌 Check out Presqu’ile Provincial park (free park pass included with your stay) for the perfect summer day trip including a sandy beach to relax on or many trails to explore

🌅If you are looking for a cute spot for a meal with a view head to the Harborview Marina Restaurant! Just steps from the cottage with amazing food and drinks 

😌Wanting to just chill and relax? The cottage has a full patio set with a bbq and any kitchen/bathroom essentials you are looking for! We loved starting the fire just after sunset to enjoy the view with some snacks to wind down!
